  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo Controlled, Parallel-group Study, Comparing Ivermectin Lotion, 0.5% in the Treatment of Subjects With Active Infestation With Head Lice and Their Ova</official_title>
