  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo controlled, Parallel-group study, comparing
      Ivermectin Lotion, 0.5%
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo controlled, Parallel-group study, comparing
      Ivermectin Lotion, 0.5% to Sklice (Ivermectin) Lotion, 0.5% and both active treatment to a
      placebo control in the treatment of subjects with active infestation with head lice and their
      Ova
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
